# CODEOWNERS — mallcop self-extension frozen paths
#
# Written into the operator's fork by `mallcop init --pro` (or
# `mallcop selfext --scaffold-gha`). This is a BELT to the in-runner guard
# stage (core/selfgate/guard.go), which already HARD-REJECTS any authored diff
# touching these prefixes. Even a malicious .github/ PR needs the operator's own
# review; the committee/grader/corpus stay maintainer-only upstream.
#
# Replace @operator with the fork owner's GitHub handle before you enable branch
# protection (see the scaffold checklist).

# The CI / workflow surface — an authored PR must never touch the gate that judges it.
/.github/                @operator

# The committee (consensus-not-rules floor), the eval grader, and the self-ext guard.
/core/agent/             @operator
/core/eval/              @operator
/core/selfgate/          @operator

# The held-out exam scenarios that exam-detect grades against.
/exams/scenarios/        @operator
